⍝ Decode.tc
⍝ ═════════

      ⎕IO←1

      ⍝ GNU APL: ⊥ is Decode (IBM APL2 calls this ⊤)
      ⍝ Precond: A B Z simple numeric
      ⍝ inv: ⍴Z ←→ (¯1↓⍴A),1↓⍴B
      A ← ⎕RVAL 2 (3 4) (,0 1 0 0 0)        ⍝ 3×4 radix matrix
      B ← ⎕RVAL 2 (4 5) (,0 1 0 0 0)        ⍝ 4×5 digits matrix
      Z ← A⊥B
      (⍴Z) ≡ (¯1↓⍴A),1↓⍴B
1
      ⍝ inv: ⍴⍴Z ←→ (0⌈¯1+⍴⍴A)+(0⌈¯1+⍴⍴B)
      (⍴⍴Z) ≡ ,(0⌈¯1+⍴⍴A)+(0⌈¯1+⍴⍴B)
1
